  "body": "<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/072fcab02c62544a.jpg?v=1782527851\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>Happy Friday, friends! In case you didn't know, I used to wear a tee shirt and jeans every single day. While I am still all about comfort, I want to take it up a notch and this outfit might just be the trick. The whole outfit is from <a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?B=286192&amp;U=530666&amp;M=31374&amp;urllink=\">Cents of Style</a> and the super soft tunic is just <a href=\"http://shareasale.com/u.cfm?d=405095&amp;m=31374&amp;u=530666&amp;afftrack=\">$19.95 + FREE SHIPPING w/code TOPSTORY</a> through 3/26. I paired it with pants similar to these, which have a bunch of holes in them but the colored denim make them feel fresh and fun for spring.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"7b-Amy+Tangerine+_+Cents+of+Style+Tunic.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/1f21f0a0aaa8b678.jpg?v=1782527854\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"7c-Cents+of+Style+x+Amy+Tangerine+_+Photos+by+Ann-Marie+Espinoza.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/458704220c6ae45c.jpg?v=1782527857\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"7d-Cents+of+Style+x+Amy+Tangerine+_+Photos+by+Ann-Marie+Espinoza.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/416fe64fac3c0b29.jpg?v=1782527860\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"7e-Cents+of+Style+x+Amy+Tangerine+_+Photos+by+Ann-Marie+Espinoza.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/0872900abe6d7103.jpg?v=1782527862\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"7f-Cents+of+Style+x+Amy+Tangerine+_+Photos+by+Ann-Marie+Espinoza.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/d41240e2b3a28ccc.jpg?v=1782527865\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"7g-Cents+of+Style+x+Amy+Tangerine+_+Photos+by+Ann-Marie+Espinoza.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/5212310d444f94fb.jpg?v=1782527868\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"7h-Cents+of+Style+x+Amy+Tangerine+_+Photos+by+Ann-Marie+Espinoza.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/8b956c806e2c4c66.jpg?v=1782527871\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"7i-Cents+of+Style+x+Amy+Tangerine+_+Photos+by+Ann-Marie+Espinoza.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/8b93f8f713850bdc.jpg?v=1782527874\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>Location: <a href=\"https://www.tomdixon.net/\">TOM DIXON</a> at Platform LA | Photos by <a href=\"http://annmarieloves.com/\">Ann-Marie</a></p><p>So many sizes and colors available, I might have to stock up multiple colors of these babydoll tunics! Through 3/26 the tunics are just <a href=\"http://shareasale.com/u.cfm?d=405095&amp;m=31374&amp;u=530666&amp;afftrack=\">$19.95 + FREE SHIPPING w/code TOPSTORY</a>! </p>"
